🌡️ Temperature Compensation Calibration (Eddy USB Only)

This command include autotemp for better calibrattion

Run:

	PROBE_EDDY_TEMP_CALIBRATE

When prompted, use the paper method to pinch the paper between the nozzle and the bed and click accept. And continue to finish

SAVE_CONFIG

If the printer does not have the enclosure, edit /config/options/probe/eddy_tap.cfg. Search [gcode PROBE_EDDY_TEMP_CALIBRATE]

Change TARGET=70 to TARGET=50

Finish:

Run:

G28

QGL

BED_MESH_CALIBRATE

Save_Config

Try with:

TAP_HOME

